    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "旧沙发、褪色的窗帘、踩出来的地板痕迹——三样东西指向同一个结论：Rose在那间地下室住了至少五年。不是你说的'不到一年'。",
    "enWords": "The worn sofa, the sun-bleached curtains, the foot-worn floor — three pieces of evidence pointing to one conclusion: Rose has been living in that basement for at least five years. Not the 'less than a year' you claimed.",
